Google X CEO Astro Teller on the Next Moonshot By Google | This Sunday (9/29) BSCF Tech & Entrepreneurship Forum

 
 
Want to join the next moonshot at Google? Meet Astro Teller, CEO at Google X, who is coming to BSCF2019 on Sep28 at UC Berkeley! Identify the next big opportunity and learn about building impactful projects! See our facebook event at: https://www.facebook.com/events/971266173227804/

About this event:
The keynote speech Astro Teller, CEO at Google X, is part of BSCF, a day-long tech&entrepreneurship conference that hosts 1k+ audiences and 20+ speakers. Don't miss the opportunities to meet top entrepreneurs from the bay area! See more information on our website: bscf.io

Key Takeaways:
- The coolest project & next moonshot that Google is working on
- Google X CEO's career advice: on joining Google and being impactful within a huge company
- Google X's vision on the future of technology
 
Join us at BSCF 2019 this Sunday (9/29) at Wheeler Auditorium!
__
posted on behalf of students organizations from Berkeley and Stanford and alumni networks.
